author: The Piano Guys
description:
Jon is stepping back into the world of solo acoustic shows—something deeply personal and close to his heart. These concerts will be intimate, unplugged evenings with just Jon, a piano, a bench, and you! You’ll hear the music that started it all, fan favorites, and the stories behind them in a more personal setting than ever before.

🎟️ Tickets on sale in our bio!
title: Jon Solo Tour
